data.description: Beacon Beauty! 3BR 1.5 bath end unit Townhome in the Villas at Fishkill Creek Community. 1st floor features include an updated eat in kitchen with granite countertops, tiled backsplash, ceramic tile floors and stainless appliances. Large, bright and inviting living room with split unit A/C, hardwood floors and sliding glass doors to deck that overlooks the Fishkill Creek. Laundry and powder room on Main Level. Second floor features large primary BR with walk in closet, 2 additional bedrooms and a full bath. Conveniently located a half mile from Beacon's booming Main street with Art galleries, Antiques, unique shops and eateries, only 2 miles to the Beacon Train Station and minutes to highways. A wonderful opportunity!
